c: 67
v: 5
t: Phir dohra ker do do baar dekhley teri nigah teri taraf zalil(o-aajiz) hoker thaki hui lot aayegi.Be-shak hum ney aasman duniya ko chiraghon (sitaron) say aarasta kiya aur enehn shetanon kay maarnay ka zariya banadiya aur shetanon kay liye hum ney (dozakh ka jalanay wala) azab tayyar kerdiya